Symbol.Script_3D:
h_1=0 h_2=0
PEN gs_cont_pen
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 THEN dw=0 dp=0 ENDIF
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 THEN END IF gs_shadow=0 THEN SHADOW off
MATERIAL gs_ibeam_mat
!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!! COLUMN !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!! Unid=1
!!! *** Length
IF ang THEN HOTSPOT 0, 0, rh-he/2, unID, a, 1+128 : unID=unID+1 IF NOT(ang) THEN HOTSPOT 0, 0, rh-he/2, unID, a, 1+256 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT -1, 0, rh-he/2, unID, a, 3 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT a, 0, rh-he/2, unID, a, 2 : unID=unID+1
!!! *** Height
HOTSPOT a, 0, 0, unID, rh, 1+128 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT a, 0, -1, unID, rh, 3 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT a, 0, rh, unID, rh, 2 : unID=unID+1
FOR I=-1 TO 1 STEP 2 HOTSPOT 0, I*b/2, 0, unID, ang, 6 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT +1, I*b/2, 0, unID, ang, 4+128 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0, -1+I*b/2, 0, unID, ang, 7 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT (a/2)-0.15, I*b/2, 0+((a/2)-0.15)*TAN(ang), unID, ang, 5 : unID=unID+1 NEXT I
!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!! BEAMS !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!
FOR I=1 TO numofbeam-1 PUT BEAMLENGTH[I] NEXT I PUT BEAMLENGTH[9] PUT hs FOR I=1 TO numofbeam-1 PUT SECTHEIGHT[I] NEXT I PUT he
ROTy 90-rot_p
FOR I=1 TO numofbeam
IF I=1 THEN b_1=0 IF I=2 THEN b_1=USE (1) IF I>2 THEN PUT GET (I-2) b_1=USE (1) PUT GET (NSP-I+2) ENDIF
IF I>1 THEN PUT GET (I-1) b_2=USE (1) PUT GET (NSP-I+1)
PUT GET (numofbeam+I-1) h_1=USE (1) PUT GET (NSP-(numofbeam+I-1))
PUT GET (numofbeam+I) h_2=USE (1) PUT GET (NSP-(numofbeam+I))
ADDz b_1
CALL "I-Beam Slope" PARAMETERS a=ap, b=b_2, gs_ibeam_mat=gs_ibeam_mat, h_1=h_1, h_2=h_2, dp=dp, dw=dw, sp=(sp=1)*(I=1), ep=(I=numofbeam)*(ep=1), cut1=-rot_p*(I=1), cut2=-rot_p*(I=numofbeam), cutp1=((BETA[I]+90+GAMMA[I+1]-180))*(I>1), cutp2=((BETA[I+1]+90+GAMMA[I+2]-180))*(I<numofbeam), rot_p=0
NEXT I DEL numofbeam
DEL 1
!!! *** Profile Height in Start Section
HOTSPOT 0, 0, 0, unID, hs, 1+128 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0, 0, 1, unID, hs, 3 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0, 0, -hs, unID, hs, 2 : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT btotal*COS(rot_p), 0, btotal*SIN(rot_p), unID, he, 1+128 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT btotal*COS(rot_p), 0, btotal*SIN(rot_p)+1, unID, he, 3 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT btotal*COS(rot_p), 0, btotal*SIN(rot_p)-he, unID, he, 2 : unID=unID+1
ROTy -rot_p
IF numofbeam>1 THEN HOTSPOT b1p, 0, 0, unID, h1, 1+128 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT b1p, 0, 1, unID, h1, 3 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT b1p, 0, -h1, unID, h1, 2 : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT 0, 0, 0, unID, b1p, 1+128 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT -1, 0, 0, unID, b1p, 3 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT b1p, 0, 0, unID, b1p, 2 : unID=unID+1 ENDIF
IF numofbeam>2 THEN HOTSPOT b2p, 0, 0, unID, h2, 1+128 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT b2p, 0, 1, unID, h2, 3 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT b2p, 0, -h2, unID, h2, 2 : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT 0, 0, 0, unID, b2p, 1+128 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT -1, 0, 0, unID, b2p, 3 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT b2p, 0, 0, unID, b2p, 2 : unID=unID+1 ENDIF
IF numofbeam>3 THEN HOTSPOT b3p, 0, 0, unID, h3, 1+128 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT b3p, 0, 1, unID, h3, 3 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT b3p, 0, -h3, unID, h3, 2 : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT 0, 0, 0, unID, b3p, 1+128 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT -1, 0, 0, unID, b3p, 3 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT b3p, 0, 0, unID, b3p, 2 : unID=unID+1 ENDIF
IF numofbeam>4 THEN HOTSPOT b4p, 0, 0, unID, h4, 1+128 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT b4p, 0, 1, unID, h4, 3 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT b4p, 0, -h4, unID, h4, 2 : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT 0, 0, 0, unID, b4p, 1+128 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT -1, 0, 0, unID, b4p, 3 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT b4p, 0, 0, unID, b4p, 2 : unID=unID+1 ENDIF
IF numofbeam>5 THEN HOTSPOT b5p, 0, 0, unID, h5, 1+128 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT b5p, 0, 1, unID, h5, 3 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT b5p, 0, -h5, unID, h5, 2 : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT 0, 0, 0, unID, b5p, 1+128 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT -1, 0, 0, unID, b5p, 3 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT b5p, 0, 0, unID, b5p, 2 : unID=unID+1 ENDIF
IF numofbeam>6 THEN HOTSPOT b6p, 0, 0, unID, h6, 1+128 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT b6p, 0, 1, unID, h6, 3 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT b6p, 0, -h6, unID, h6, 2 : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT 0, 0, 0, unID, b6p, 1+128 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT -1, 0, 0, unID, b6p, 3 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT b6p, 0, 0, unID, b6p, 2 : unID=unID+1 ENDIF
IF numofbeam>7 THEN HOTSPOT b7p, 0, 0, unID, h7, 1+128 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT b7p, 0, 1, unID, h7, 3 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT b7p, 0, -h7, unID, h7, 2 : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT 0, 0, 0, unID, b7p, 1+128 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT -1, 0, 0, unID, b7p, 3 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT b7p, 0, 0, unID, b7p, 2 : unID=unID+1 ENDIF
IF numofbeam>8 THEN HOTSPOT b8p, 0, 0, unID, h8, 1+128 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT b8p, 0, 1, unID, h8, 3 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT b8p, 0, -h8, unID, h8, 2 : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT 0, 0, 0, unID, b8p, 1+128 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT -1, 0, 0, unID, b8p, 3 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT b8p, 0, 0, unID, b8p, 2 : unID=unID+1 ENDIF
DEL 1
Symbol.Script_2D:
PEN gs_cont_pen FILL gs_fill_type
Unid=1 hLineID = 1000
!!! *** Length
HOTSPOT2 0, 0, unID, A, 1+256 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 -1, 0, unID, A, 3 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 A, 0, unID, A, 2 : unID=unID+1
!!! *** Length/2
HOTSPOT2 A/2,0,unID : unID=unID+1
!!! *** Frame Width IF only_axis=0 THEN
HOTSPOT2 A,0,unID,B2,1+128, B : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 A,-b2,unID,B2,2, B : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 A,1,unID,B2,3, B : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT2 A,0,unID,B2,1+128, B : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 A,b2,unID,B2,2, B : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 A,-1,unID,B2,3, B : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT2 0,0,unID,B2,1+128, B : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 0,-b2,unID,B2,2, B : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 0,1,unID,B2,3, B : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT2 0,0,unID,B2,1+128, B : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 0,b2,unID,B2,2, B : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 0,-1,unID,B2,3, B : unID=unID+1
ENDIF
HOTLINE2 0, 0, a, 0, hLineID
IF only_axis=0 THEN
POLY2_B 5, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, 0, -b/2, 1, 0, b/2, 1, a, b/2, 1, a, -b/2, 1, 0, -b/2, -1
IF gs_detlevel_2D_m = 2 THEN LINE_TYPE DetailLineType FOR I=-1 TO 1 STEP 2 MUL2 1, I ADD2 0, dw/2 LINE2 0, 0, a, 0 DEL 2 NEXT I ENDIF
ENDIF
IF axis THEN PEN axis_pen LINE_TYPE axis_line_type LINE2 0, 0, a, 0 ENDIF
Symbol.Script_1D:
EPS=0.0001
VALUES "numofbeam" RANGE [1, 9]
ap=b
h_1=0 h_2=0 IF GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "ang" THEN rh = (A)*TAN(ang) : rot_p = ang PARAMETERS rh = rh ELSE rot_p=ATN((rh)/(a)) : ang = rot_p PARAMETERS ang = ang ENDIF
btotal=(a)/COS(rot_p)
DIM BEAMLENGTH_0[] BEAMLENGTH_0[1]=b1p BEAMLENGTH_0[2]=b2p BEAMLENGTH_0[3]=b3p BEAMLENGTH_0[4]=b4p BEAMLENGTH_0[5]=b5p BEAMLENGTH_0[6]=b6p BEAMLENGTH_0[7]=b7p BEAMLENGTH_0[8]=b8p BEAMLENGTH_0[9]=btotal
IF GLOB_MODPAR_NAME="numofbeam" OR GLOB_MODPAR_NAME="A" THEN
IF numofbeam>=1 THEN : b1p=btotal/numofbeam : ELSE : b1p=0 : ENDIF IF numofbeam>=2 THEN : b2p=btotal/numofbeam+b1p : ELSE : b2p=0 : ENDIF IF numofbeam>=3 THEN : b3p=btotal/numofbeam+b2p : ELSE : b3p=0 : ENDIF IF numofbeam>=4 THEN : b4p=btotal/numofbeam+b3p : ELSE : b4p=0 : ENDIF IF numofbeam>=5 THEN : b5p=btotal/numofbeam+b4p : ELSE : b5p=0 : ENDIF IF numofbeam>=6 THEN : b6p=btotal/numofbeam+b5p : ELSE : b6p=0 : ENDIF IF numofbeam>=7 THEN : b7p=btotal/numofbeam+b6p : ELSE : b7p=0 : ENDIF IF numofbeam>=8 THEN : b8p=btotal/numofbeam+b7p : ELSE : b8p=0 : ENDIF
IF numofbeam>=1 THEN : PARAMETERS b1p=btotal/numofbeam : ELSE : PARAMETERS b1p=0 : ENDIF IF numofbeam>=2 THEN : PARAMETERS b2p=btotal/numofbeam+b1p : ELSE : PARAMETERS b2p=0 : ENDIF IF numofbeam>=3 THEN : PARAMETERS b3p=btotal/numofbeam+b2p : ELSE : PARAMETERS b3p=0 : ENDIF IF numofbeam>=4 THEN : PARAMETERS b4p=btotal/numofbeam+b3p : ELSE : PARAMETERS b4p=0 : ENDIF IF numofbeam>=5 THEN : PARAMETERS b5p=btotal/numofbeam+b4p : ELSE : PARAMETERS b5p=0 : ENDIF IF numofbeam>=6 THEN : PARAMETERS b6p=btotal/numofbeam+b5p : ELSE : PARAMETERS b6p=0 : ENDIF IF numofbeam>=7 THEN : PARAMETERS b7p=btotal/numofbeam+b6p : ELSE : PARAMETERS b7p=0 : ENDIF IF numofbeam>=8 THEN : PARAMETERS b8p=btotal/numofbeam+b7p : ELSE : PARAMETERS b8p=0 : ENDIF
hs=0.2 h1=0.2 h2=0.2 h3=0.2 h4=0.2 h5=0.2 h6=0.2 h7=0.2 h8=0.2 he=0.2
PARAMETERS hs=0.2 PARAMETERS h1=0.2 PARAMETERS h2=0.2 PARAMETERS h3=0.2 PARAMETERS h4=0.2 PARAMETERS h5=0.2 PARAMETERS h6=0.2 PARAMETERS h7=0.2 PARAMETERS h8=0.2 PARAMETERS he=0.2
ENDIF
DIM BEAMLENGTH[] BEAMLENGTH[1]=b1p BEAMLENGTH[2]=b2p-b1p BEAMLENGTH[3]=b3p-b2p BEAMLENGTH[4]=b4p-b3p BEAMLENGTH[5]=b5p-b4p BEAMLENGTH[6]=b6p-b5p BEAMLENGTH[7]=b7p-b6p BEAMLENGTH[8]=b8p-b7p IF numofbeam>1 THEN BEAMLENGTH[9]=btotal-BEAMLENGTH_0[numofbeam-1] ELSE BEAMLENGTH[9]=btotal ENDIF
DIM SECTHEIGHT[] SECTHEIGHT[1]=h1 SECTHEIGHT[2]=h2 SECTHEIGHT[3]=h3 SECTHEIGHT[4]=h4 SECTHEIGHT[5]=h5 SECTHEIGHT[6]=h6 SECTHEIGHT[7]=h7 SECTHEIGHT[8]=h8
DIM BETA[] !!!! gerendak also lemezeinek hajlasszogei
BETA[1]=-ATN((hs*COS(rot_p)-h1)/(BEAMLENGTH[1]+hs*SIN(rot_p))) BETA[2]=ATN((hs*COS(rot_p)-h1)/(BEAMLENGTH[1]+hs*SIN(rot_p)))
FOR I=3 TO numofbeam IF ABS(BEAMLENGTH[I-1]-0)>0.0001 THEN BETA[I]=ATN((SECTHEIGHT[I-2]-SECTHEIGHT[I-1])/(BEAMLENGTH[I-1])) NEXT I
IF numofbeam>1 & (abs((BEAMLENGTH[9]-he*SIN(rot_p))) > EPS) THEN BETA[numofbeam+1]=ATN((SECTHEIGHT[numofbeam-1]-he*COS(rot_p))/(BEAMLENGTH[9]-he*SIN(rot_p))) IF numofbeam=1 THEN BETA[numofbeam+1]=ATN((hs-he*COS(rot_p))/(BEAMLENGTH[9]-he*SIN(rot_p)))
IF numofbeam<9 THEN FOR I=numofbeam+2 TO 10 BETA[I]=0 NEXT I ENDIF
DIM GAMMA[] !!!! Szogfelezok GAMMA[1]=10 GAMMA[2]=(180-BETA[1]+BETA[2])/2 GAMMA[3]=(180-BETA[2]+BETA[3])/2 GAMMA[4]=(180-BETA[3]+BETA[4])/2 GAMMA[5]=(180-BETA[4]+BETA[5])/2 GAMMA[6]=(180-BETA[5]+BETA[6])/2 GAMMA[7]=(180-BETA[6]+BETA[7])/2 GAMMA[8]=(180-BETA[7]+BETA[8])/2 GAMMA[9]=(180-BETA[8]+BETA[9])/2 GAMMA[10]=(180-BETA[9]+BETA[10])/2
GAMMA[numofbeam+1]=(180-BETA[numofbeam]+BETA[numofbeam+1])/2
